'''脫氧劑'''一般放置在多孔[[香包|小袋]]中，多孔[[香包|小袋]]再被放置入密閉的商品[[包装|包装]]中<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Modeling of oxygen scavenging for improved barrier behavior: Blend films|url=http://www.stc-clips.org/site/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Modeling-of-oxygen-scavenging-for-improved-barrier-behavior.pdf|last=Ferrari|first=M C|last2=S. Carranzaa|journal=Journal of Membrane Science|accessdate=20 Sep 2013|issue=|doi=10.1016/j.memsci.2008.12.030|year=2009|volume=329|pages=183–192|language=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927061248/http://www.stc-clips.org/site/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/Modeling-of-oxygen-scavenging-for-improved-barrier-behavior.pdf|archivedate=27 September 2013|last3=R.T. Bonnecazea|last4=K.K. Tunga|last5=B.D. Freemana|last6=D.R. Paula}}</ref>，以帮助減少包装內的[[氧气|氧气]]含量，這樣可以延长商品的[[保质期|保质期]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Evaluation of the performance of iron-based oxygen scavengers, with comments on their optimal applications|last=Miltz|first=J.|last2=Perry|first2=M.|journal=Packaging Technology and Science|doi=10.1002/pts.671|year=2005|volume=18|pages=21–27|pmc=|pmid=}}</ref>。脫氧劑主要成分有铁粉和[[氯化钠|氯化钠]]的混合物<ref name="EPT" />以及[[活性炭|活性炭]]。鐵粉接觸氧氣後會[[氧化|氧化]]形成[[氧化铁|氧化铁]]。为了幫助鐵進行氧化，氯化钠被添加進來，作为[[催化剂|催化剂]]或[[活化剂|活化剂]]，使铁粉即使在相对较低的[[湿度|湿度]]下也能氧化。由于氧气被消耗並與鐵粉反應形成氧化铁，包裝內的氧气含量会降低至0.01%以下 <ref name="doi10.1046/j.1365-2621.2002.00558.x">{{Cite journal|title=Absorption kinetics of oxygen scavengers|last=Tewari|first=G.|last2=Jayas|first2=D. S.|journal=International Journal of Food Science and Technology|issue=2|doi=10.1046/j.1365-2621.2002.00558.x|year=2002|volume=37|pages=209–217|pmc=|pmid=|last3=Jeremiah|first3=L. E.|last4=Holley|first4=R. A.}}</ref><ref name="MacDonald">{{Cite web|title=Oxygen Absorbers Facts|url=http://sorbentsystems.com/Oxygen_Absorber_Facts.pdf|accessdate=August 2013|author=MacDonald|first=Jameyson|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202195507/https://www.sorbentsystems.com/Oxygen_Absorber_Facts.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1克铁完全氧化後可以去除包裝內300立方厘米的氧气。虽然其他物質也能去除氧氣，但是铁是最有用的，因为它不会像[[硫化物|硫化物]]那样产生气味，也不会像{{link-en|铝化物|Aluminide}}那样容易[[钝化|钝化]]。其他能作為脫氧劑的物質也很難符合食品安全要求<ref name="EPT">{{cite book | isbn = 9780470087046 | title = Encyclopedia of Packaging Technology | url = https://archive.org/details/wileyencyclopedi00yamk | editor1-last = Yam | editor1-first= K. L. | year = 2009 | publisher = John Wiley & Sons  | pages = [https://archive.org/details/wileyencyclopedi00yamk/page/842 842]–850  }}</ref>。[[活性炭|活性炭]]則能[[吸附|吸附]]一些气体和[[有机分子|有机分子]]，從而使商品不再含有異味。

